 @{fg shine}Contents of the Archive@{fg text}

 o  1oo_clog.rexx        - heart of the program

 o  1oo_clog.cfg         - the @{"configuration" link "CFG_Online" 0} file

 o  1oo_clog.chat        - notifies 1oo_clog.rexx if there's been a chat,
                           both sysop & inter-user (small external program
                           for speed reasons)

 o  1oo_clog.cookie      - some @{"cookies" link "CFG_Cookies" 0} (taglines) displayed at the bottom of
                           the last callers list

 o  1oo_clog.data        - the actual logfile (updated during logoff)

 o  1oo_clog.guide       - this guidefile

 o  1oo_clog.stat        - statistics file

 o  sys.cloglogo         - plain ascii @{"logo" link "CFG_Logos" 0}

 o  tt2.cloglogo         - ibmgfx @{"logo" link "CFG_Logos" 0}, 16 colors

 o  tt3.cloglogo         - isogfx @{"logo" link "CFG_Logos" 0}, 8 colors


 Besides that, you might find some example pictures and other complete
 useless crap like bbs adds and stuff... :)
@endnode

